org.semanticweb.owlapi.profiles

Enum Profiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Profiles>
      • org.semanticweb.owlapi.profiles.Profiles
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Profiles>, HasIRI, OWLProfile

    public enum Profiles
extends Enum<Profiles>
implements HasIRI, OWLProfile
    This enumeration includes all currently implemented profile checkers and known information about available reasoners for those profiles. Note that reasoner capabilities might be out of date, since they are independent projects. Therefore, ther emight be reasoners not listed here and the reasoners listed might have changed.
    The use case for this class was suggested by Peter Ansell, see patch set 1 and patch set 2.
    Notice that the OWLProfiles referred here are stateless, therefore only one instance needs to be created and can be reused across threads.
    Author:
    ignazio

      • supportingReasoners

        public Collection<String> supportingReasoners()
        Returns:
        collection of OWLReasonerFactory class names known to support the expressivity of this profile. The factories can be instantiated through instantiateFactory() if the reasoner classes are on the classpath. Note that this list is provided for information only, and might be incorrect or incomplete due to changes in the reasoner implementations.
        Should you know of a reasoner not mentioned here, or find an error in the reported supported profiles, please raise a bug about it.

      • instantiateFactory

        public static OWLReasonerFactory instantiateFactory(String factoryClassName)
        Parameters:
        factoryClassName - class name to instantiate
        Returns:
        an OWLReasonerFactory if the class name represents an OWLReasonerFactory implementation available on the classpath. Any exception raised by Class.forName(factoryClassName) is wrapped by an OWLRuntimeException.
